Cell.Text: Greetings traveller, may we speak?

My name is Haj-Xul, but you may call me Haj. I am a representative of a group called the An-Xileel from Black Marsh. | I have been after a wanted Telvani mage from the mainland called Zirath Ryon for some time. | I have managed to track him down to this island, Solstheim, and could use some assistance in bringing him to justice.
Alright, I'll help. Do you have any leads?

Thank you stranger. I've found that my target boarded a ship headed straight to Raven Rock some time ago. | Except he never arrived, and neither did his ship, it wrecked short of the coast. | Conveniently close to the coast, actually, so we are going to go check the wreckage for any clues.
What's in it for me?
I would be willing to share a cut of the bounty with you. It's rather large as you can imagine.
Why are you after him?

You must understand, we would normally avoid going after criminals outside our territory, but this is a special case. | This... man... is responsible for countless atrocities against my people from the time when slavery was commonplace in Morrowind. | We also have reason to believe he might be plotting to get back at us for our actions in the mainland. | He must be stopped.
Lead the way.
[S] G|Follow me, it's not far from here.
Sorry, I'd rather stay out of this.
[S] G|I understand, I'll keep an eye on this dock for a while longer. Let me know if you change your mind.
Have you changed your mind?
Here it is, and it looks like someone beat us to it. We'll have to deal with them before we can search the place.
Let's do this!
[S] G|May the Hist guide our hands.
Wait! Let me handle them myself.
You wish to deal with them yourself? Are you sure?
Yes, they won't see me coming.
[S] G|As you wish, I'll await your return...
No, you are right, let's fight together.
[S] G|May the Hist guide our hands.
Keep an eye out for any clues, they must have left something behind.
(hand over the journal) I found something.

[S] G|Let me see that. | Hmm.. I see... | Aha, I knew it! The whole thing was a set-up! | Looks like our friend here hired himself some muscle. | Running scared Zirath? You won’t go far now... | Traveler, we must chase after them! The journal tells of the location of their hideout. Why don’t you lead the way this time?
Our friend here is in bad shape, I'll need to see to her wounds. | Could you look for any clues as to where Zirath might have gone? There must be something we can use.
[S] G|I can take care of this. Go search for clues, we can't remain here long, she'll need proper care.

Node.Caption: RE01MiasmaQstCheckingOnPrisoner02Topic01: Is there anything I can do to help?

Cell.Text: [S] G|

Node.Caption: RE01MiasmaQstCheckingOnPrisoner02Topic02: Alright, I'll let you know once I find anything.

Cell.Text: Have you found anything? We need to hurry.
Not yet.
G|Keep searching, there must be something we can use.
(Show research notes) I found these notes.

Let me see that. | He left a journal?! Telvani ego truly knows no limits. | This speaks of an ancient prison to the west, no doubt a nordic ruin from the sound of it. | (sigh) Friend, I hate to ask for even more after all you've done so far but I need you to go after him alone. | This woman will die without proper care so I must return to Raven Rock, but we also can't let him reach whatever it is he hopes to find there.

I have contacts that I can call upon to get her to a safe place. Noone will argue with a diplomatic envoy over something like this. | Look, I would want nothing more than to continue my hunt but I can't leave a fellow Saxhleel to die while doing so. | So I am asking you, finish my quest and bring that monster to justice. | We simply cannot risk letting him get away... or worse, what he's looking for.

Node.Caption: RE01MiasmaQstResearchNotesFound02Topic01: Can't I be the one to take her to Raven Rock?

Cell.Text: [S] G|Are you serious?! Fine! I’ll triple it if that’s what it takes, just go after him!

Node.Caption: RE01MiasmaQstResearchNotesFound02Topic02: What about my reward? This is more than I bargained for.

Cell.Text: [S] G|You have my thanks friend but be careful, I don’t know what you might find in such a place.

Node.Caption: RE01MiasmaQstResearchNotesFound02Topic03: Alright, I will go after him.
